genresAdvancedInfo.name: zim gospel
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Zim gospel is a genre of music that originated in Zimbabwe and is characterized by its religious themes and African rhythms. The lyrics are often centered around praising God and spreading the gospel message. The music has a powerful and uplifting effect on listeners, and it is widely popular in Zimbabwe and other African countries.
